  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV44">
<l>pāliṉīrmai cempoṉīrmai pāciyiṉpa cumpuṟam</l>
<l>pōlunīrmai poṟpuṭaitta ṭattuvaṇṭu viṇṭulā</l>
<l>nīlanīrmai yeṉṟivaini ṟaintakāla nāṉkumāy</l>
<l>māliṉīrmai vaiyakamma ṟaittateṉṉa nīrmaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is th[is] nature that consist in [having this] world hide the [affable] nature of Māl,</l>
<l>[the lord] of all four time [frames] filled with these, [namely],</l>
<l>the [white] nature of the milk, the [red] nature of red gold,</l>
<l>the [green] nature akin to the outer green of the moss,</l>
<l>the [blue] nature of the blue nelumbo in the pretty pond</l>
<l rend="indent">[around] which bees open [their wings] and roam?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
